{"tid":1975062,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特拿不到現金！西方石油 (OXY) 改派股票股利","createTime":"2020-04-16T09:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T13:18:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b172291c4ee73a4584cd541c25f29152c0c28a98","tid":1975062,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"巴菲特拿不到現金！西方石油改派股票股利<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3135511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3135511&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10IWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=f371999c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3135511&h=a07d8503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3135511</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕國際油價暴跌，美國能源股也慘兮兮，美國石油和天然氣公司西方石油公司（Occidental Petroleum）股價崩跌，公司現金流更面臨壓力，西方石油公司也決定改用股票股利，來支付「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）旗下波克夏海瑟威（Berkshire Hathaway，下稱波克夏）股利，而不是原定的現金股利方式。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>《路透》報導，根據週三（15日）提交給監管機構的文件，西方石油公司以普通股來支付給波克夏的2億美元季度股利，若以西方石油公司週二（14日）收盤價14.90美元計算，這筆給波克夏的股票約價值2.57億美元，比原本要給波克夏的2億美元現金股利來得高。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>波克夏可以馬上出售這筆股票，但波克夏尚未表明其意圖。文件顯示，波克夏目前持有西方石油公司約4.7%股份。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n波克夏和西方石油公司拒絕評論。<br />\n<br />\n波克夏去年4月投資西方石油公司100億美元，換取西方石油公司的特別股，這些特別股年息8%，也就是季度股利達2億美元，並取得認股權憑證。但西方石油公司必須完成阿納達科石油公司（Anadarko Petroleum）的併購案。最終西方石油公司在巴菲特的資金奧援下，擊敗了雪佛龍（Chevron），以570億美元併購了阿納達科石油公司。<br />\n<br />\n但今年油價崩跌，西方石油公司資產負債表壓力大增，股價也重挫，支付股票股利對西方石油公司來說，可能是個痛苦的決定，在收購阿納達科時，股價還有60美元左右水準，但之後緩步走低，西方石油公司股價週三收在13.61美元，今年迄今股價已下跌約68%，公司市值僅剩120億美元左右。"},{"pid":"89341b621cd14c8eb54eec756df6576b16922abc","tid":1975062,"uid":278264,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"裸泳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />OXY會唔會破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9070abf13e84d349d3bb72ee0f7caf00c833f30e","tid":1975062,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6add253fb6f732d8e1ae5f356cd06874278e0061","tid":1975062,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />財技"},{"pid":"d00a318aed21ffaa09b4a183453bc859d18be36b","tid":1975062,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9070abf13e84d349d3bb72ee0f7caf00c833f30e","tid":1975062,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正最後受傷既都係老散 WFC"},{"pid":"1e30f52cebae2a755f84471c3cd809982878d321","tid":1975062,"uid":77187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"大把連登仔晚晚幫廢佬接貨 oxy價值投資gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7520f6c51cb03438213d5835647ff5bfad48da7","tid":1975062,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f93199f7ade6405aa6ee7daf8d66c692f22a179e","tid":1975062,"uid":125888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"你不會投資？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383480fe3057b98943797d463856a6420142fd0c","tid":1975062,"uid":159313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"你有沒有想過  讓巴菲特跟你一起裸泳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"